      • setUp

        public void setUp()
        Sets initial variables to a well-defined initial value.

        Assigns a Guest object to the ot instance variable with the name "Ot" and assigns a Guest object to the sien instance variable with the name "Sien". Also assigns Room objects to instance variables k101 and k102 with numbers 101 and 102 respectively. Lastly, checks in sien in room k102.

      • testInitialcondition

        Test if the initial condition complies to the specification.

      • testCheckinEmpty

        public void testCheckinEmpty()

      • testCheckinTaken

        public void testCheckinTaken()
        Checks checking in a new guest in a room that is already taken. Calls ot.checkin(k102).

      • testCheckoutKnown

        public void testCheckoutKnown()
        Tests checking out a guest that rented a room. Calls sien.checkout().

      • testCheckoutUnknown

        public void testCheckoutUnknown()
        Tests checking out a guest that didn't rent a room. Calls ot.checkout().
